  Navigate to Submit Request screen
  
  SYSTEM AUTO-POPULATES:
  - Name field with currentUser.name (read-only)
  - Email field with currentUser.email (read-only)
  
  DEFAULT SETTINGS:
  - Request Type: "One-time" selected
  - End Date field: Hidden
  
  OUTPUT: Display form with auto-populated fields
  
  INPUT: User selects Request Type (One-time or Recurring)
  
  IF "Recurring" selected:
    OUTPUT: Show End Date field
    OUTPUT: Change "Event Date" label to "Start Date"
  ELSE:
    OUTPUT: Hide End Date field
    OUTPUT: Keep "Event Date" label
  
  INPUT: User selects Location (school) from dropdown
  
  SYSTEM PROCESSING:
  - Filter spaces array where space.schoolId matches selected school
  - Populate Space dropdown with filtered spaces
  
  INPUT: User fills out all remaining fields
  INPUT: User optionally uploads file
